snippet.title: There Is No Game: Wrong Dimension (Nintendo Switch OFFICIAL TRAILER)
snippet.description:
Hello users. We are happy to announce that There Is No Game: Wrong Dimension is now available on Nintendo Switch! (Re)discover the non-game, get it on Switch now: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/there-is-no-game-wrong-dimension-switch/

______________________________________________

"There Is No Game: Wrong Dimension" is a Point&Click comedy adventure (and Point&Click only!) that will take you on a journey you never asked to go on, through silly and unexpected video game universes.

Get There Is No Game: Wrong Dimension on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1240210/There_Is_No_Game_Wrong_Dimension/
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/there-is-no-game-wrong-dimension-switch/
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DMAP.Ting_WD&hl=fr&gl=US
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/there-is-no-game-wd/id1539133066
